lead_paragraph: Manchester United teenager Marcus Rashford's stunning introduction to big-time football has come as no surprise to Roy Hodgson and the England manager has not ruled him out of selection for his Euro 2016 finals squad.

headline.print_headline: United Youngster Rashford on Hodgson's Mind for Euros
